            <h2 class="blog-post-title">Privacy Statement</h2>
            <p class="blog-post-meta">January 28, 2017 by <a href="#">Zahra Ghaed</a></p>

            <p>We have created this privacy statement in order demonstrate our firm commitment to privacy. The following discloses the information gathering and dissemination practices for this Android application.</p>
            <!-- <p>
